  "texts": [
    "Specifically, we expand the existing dialoguebased needs extraction system by utilizing a Large Language Model (LLM) to obtain outlines of new services.",
    "Additionally, we develop a method for generating keywords based on the extracted needs to search for software development insights within the SUCCEED system.",
    "As a case study, it executes a workflow from the automatic extraction of user needs through dialogue to the provision of development insights to developers.",
    "In the experiment, we evaluated the proposed method through a detailed analysis of each step.",
    "The results indicate that the proposed method possesses the capability to present sufficient development information in response to ideal dialogues, suggesting its potential to improve the efficiency of development-based approaches for service personalization.The remainder of this paper is organized as follows: Section 2 explains related research."
